title: The Cider House Rules (1999) Tobey Maguire
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0124315/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0124315/</a>

Beautiful adaption of John Irving's novel, with only smaller bizarre details as in 'The World According to Garp' and 'The Door in the Floor'. Tobey Maguire made several serious dramas before he became Spiderman.

This is not my rip, I found it on the net but thought it should be represented here because PirateBay only has full dvds. 

DVDrip Widescreen stereo, 656x288.


Runs well in my DivX player.
